'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #3196] on 19 December 2000 at 7:54:28 pm'!"Change Set:		FillTweak-arDate:			19 December 2000Author:			Andreas RaabA fix for flood fills which hadn't been properly tested with 'unlimited paint area == false'."!!SketchEditorMorph methodsFor: 'actions & preps' stamp: 'ar 12/19/2000 19:53'!fill: evt 	"Find the area that is the same color as where you clicked. Fill it with 	the current paint color."	| box |	evt isMouseUp		ifFalse: [^ self].	"Only fill upon mouseUp"	"would like to only invalidate the area changed, but can't find out what it is."	Cursor execute		showWhile: [			box _ paintingForm				floodFill: (self getColorFor: evt)				at: evt cursorPoint - bounds origin.			self render: (box translateBy: bounds origin)]! !